3A provides a basic layer that can run smoothly for defi applications, and provides high-quality financial services for ordinary investors around the world. Its goal is to lower the entry threshold for ordinary investors and form a low gas fee layer to simplify the user experience. At the same time, it provides a wide range of development tools from identity based scripting function to built-in cross chain interoperability. 3A will open trading on justswap in the near future, which will set off a monetary revolution in the field of defi finance..
